name: The Alien Specimen of Tahrük - Galactible™ #27
description:
Holy bug-eyed aliens! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #27, the “Alien Specimen of Tahrük!” These little mischievous creatures cause all types of problems throughout the Galactiverse but they hold mysterious powers within! The Galactic Council has offered a bounty of 1,000 Tez Crystals for any living specimen. Be careful though! These little buggers are known for escaping every containment vessel and it appears the specimen pod is malfunctioning! Your mana has been raised by +2,000,000 bits!

Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations, sound effects, and music made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2022 | galactibles.com
